u siwkay nizau pilecuhan ni Ana Brnabić (·) i Belgradenu Serbia. nalecuhan ciniza i 9 a bulad 28 a demiad 1975 a mihcaan. pahezekay niza i tabakiay a cacudadan nu Hull (University of Hull ).
micakatu cunli ( Prime Minister) nu Serbiaayza sa ci Mohammed bin Salman (·), micakat a demiad sa i 2017 a mihcaan 6 bulad 29 demiad.
